videos.headline: Radford hesitates past defender for Virginia Tech bucket
videos.description: Tyrece Radford freezes the VMI defender with a hesitation move and finishes at the rim with a layup for Virginia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Radford hesitates past defender for Virginia Tech bucket) 2020/12/3 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lewis elevates for VMI bucket vs. Virginia Tech
videos.description: Myles Lewis drops steps past the Virginia Tech defender and finishes with a layup off the glass for VMI.

videos.headline: Radford floats in and-1 for Hokies
videos.description: Tyrece Radford leans in and finishes with a layup through contact for Virginia Tech vs. VMI.
